description: This top 2% rating Chukcha purrs with a rating of 80, and a multiplier of 1x. It has a total score of 80, and confers the same amount of votes in the EtherCats DAO. The card game properties are Leverage for North, 3 for East, 8 for South, and Nine Lives for West. Chukcha has the personality suit of quant. Each Founders Series cat is part of NFT history. These fine felines represent the first verifiably random packs minted with Chainlink VRF.
